{"4370020": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "被黑手浸染的玫瑰与百合", "steam_appid": 4370020, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/1189385bbf8e93b7cfd2360377531d72.avif?t=1776562999\" width=739 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在表面平靜的家庭中，兩朵純潔的花——玫瑰與百合，靜靜綻放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，一隻「黑手」悄然伸入她們的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那位健身教練的出現，如同陰影般滲透進日常生活。你逐漸察覺，母親與姐姐的變化不再只是偶然——而是一種被引導、被侵染、被改寫的過程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾經屬於你的溫柔與信任，正在被那隻看不見的黑手一點點奪走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當玫瑰染上暗色，當百合失去純白——你是否還能阻止這場墮落？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/3fcb742667e547b7359322a75c1c8b57.avif?t=1776562999\" width=739 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>古手 冴子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的母親，38歲的全職家庭主婦。數年前與丈夫離婚，獨自撫養姐弟二人。性格開朗隨和，對你十分溫柔體貼，但她的身上，似乎隱藏著某個不為人知的秘密……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/190b16e434917f94d5f19102d514d597.avif?t=1776562999\" width=616 height=371 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>古手 撫子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的姐姐，成績優異、容貌出眾的校園人氣人物。從小與你一起長大，如今就讀於同一所高中，甚至是同班同學。她表面冷淡內向、不善言辭，但總在細微之處關心著你。然而，在她心中，似乎也潛藏著某種難以言說的情感……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/f3f5d5969fbe24b66b7c550ad0e0c2c5.avif?t=1776562999\" width=616 height=371 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/98b60a77e8d6d5bbea758ea7e4d87fbc.avif?t=1776562999\" width=739 height=88 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量精美CG演出</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豐富探索與多樣事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >劇情分支由你的選擇決定</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>注意：本作包含牛頭要素，請依個人喜好審慎選擇體驗。</i></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/1189385bbf8e93b7cfd2360377531d72.avif?t=1776562999\" width=739 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在表面平靜的家庭中，兩朵純潔的花——玫瑰與百合，靜靜綻放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，一隻「黑手」悄然伸入她們的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那位健身教練的出現，如同陰影般滲透進日常生活。你逐漸察覺，母親與姐姐的變化不再只是偶然——而是一種被引導、被侵染、被改寫的過程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾經屬於你的溫柔與信任，正在被那隻看不見的黑手一點點奪走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當玫瑰染上暗色，當百合失去純白——你是否還能阻止這場墮落？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/3fcb742667e547b7359322a75c1c8b57.avif?t=1776562999\" width=739 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>古手 冴子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的母親，38歲的全職家庭主婦。數年前與丈夫離婚，獨自撫養姐弟二人。性格開朗隨和，對你十分溫柔體貼，但她的身上，似乎隱藏著某個不為人知的秘密……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/190b16e434917f94d5f19102d514d597.avif?t=1776562999\" width=616 height=371 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>古手 撫子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的姐姐，成績優異、容貌出眾的校園人氣人物。從小與你一起長大，如今就讀於同一所高中，甚至是同班同學。她表面冷淡內向、不善言辭，但總在細微之處關心著你。然而，在她心中，似乎也潛藏著某種難以言說的情感……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370020/extras/f3f5d5969fbe24b66b7